00:50:10,620 --> 00:50:13,456
- Awak teruja, bukan?
- Cepatlah jumpa dia.

864
00:50:17,835 --> 00:50:19,003
Saya kena letak jawatan?

865
00:50:19,086 --> 00:50:20,755
JABATAN SUMBER MANUSIA

